|YK0#|YKB Combat Archetypes|000

|GK0Guild and class abilities can be described through three combat
archetypes: Caster, Melee, and Hybrid. This describes how a toolkit plays; it
does not make a class into a learned guild.|000

|YK0##|YKB Caster|000

|GK0Caster toolkits have few inherent bonuses to ordinary weapon combat. They
generally have large SP pools and efficient abilities.|000

|YK0##|YKB Melee|000

|GK0Melee toolkits are almost the reverse: they have strong inherent bonuses
to combat, including additional swings.|000

|YK0##|YKB Hybrid|000

|GK0Hybrid toolkits fall in between. They have some bonuses to combat but
typically have higher SP pools than melee toolkits and more efficient
abilities.|000

